title: TTIP Trade Talks Continue Under Veil of Secrecy in Miami - Official
text: A trade official from America’s largest labor union said that chief negotiators of TTIP agreement persisted to show contempt for transparency in Miami this week by failing to provide any meaningful details to the deal’s most critical stakeholders. ...
